{"tid":2191284,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[重要] 跑100米冇15秒內唔準再冇目標咁喺危險地區鳩行","createTime":"2020-09-06T10:48:42.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-06T11:00:41.000Z","uid":218923,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"e87fe3af7d97c7062471b45a42fbde492f3dde86","tid":2191284,"uid":218923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:48:42.000Z","msg":"今日喺旺角食飯，見住個女仔原本已經跑緊，但喺2秒內比3個防暴追上㩒低。<br />\n示意圖:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rdKFrK9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrdKFrK9.png&h=a69d3b9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span class=\"red\">紅色:捉到個女仔嘅防暴</span><br />\n<span class=\"green\">綠色:原本追緊個女仔嘅防暴</span><br />\n白色:女仔<br />\n<br />\n首先喺危險地區要有番咁上吓警覺性，我諗對於10米內approach緊自己嘅物體要有警覺。<br />\n其次就係真係唔夠快。我諗個女仔喺意識到比人從橫追捕仲有~5米嘅距離，但可惜加速唔切，比人捉到<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c81394366451a99437212e34a1907ea157859d1","tid":2191284,"uid":218923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0c443326ac82316a2c92c1914552015aee6362c8","tid":2191284,"uid":218923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:51:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cd1c7793a74a12c5f64163944c55b5bc908d25d","tid":2191284,"uid":218923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:51:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51bf12acafb577b7b53d91dc2e4e97093cc001f3","tid":2191284,"uid":218923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:52:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"608675a9f14fe28a31d469b489d7251e633459dd","tid":2191284,"uid":35924,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-06T10:55:53.000Z","msg":"成年都練唔好真係唔知想點，自強下啦香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b276d493089bbabe05e9172db850c72f4721121c","tid":2191284,